      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.pjhjTVwvrN4Ly9BR]{Isolation}</p>\n<p>As long as you are in your silent state at the beginning of your turn, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to become incorporeal until the beginning of your next turn. Alternatively, if you concentrate for 1 round without spending other actions, you can spend 1 Resolve Point at the beginning of your next turn to become incorporeal for a number of rounds equal to your Wisdom modifier. You can end this incorporeal state as a swift action.</p>"
